data.description: Welcome to the 2046 sq. ft. Clifton Floor Plan with its open concept design and 3 full bedrooms. This home is light and bright with great decorator accents that make it feel like home. Tile in all high traffic areas, plantation shutters throughout, 6 panel doors, bay window in breakfast area and owner's suite, maple cabinets with pull-outs and granite in kitchen, updated bathrooms also have granite, hobby/computer room, inside laundry, water softener, covered south facing pergola patio with a knee wall and water feature, paver front courtyard, nicely landscaped and meticulously maintained.. Save with leased Solar Panels.
